前二項之未遂犯罰之。\r\n附件：\r\n聲請簡易判決處刑書","JFULLPDF":"https://data.judicial.gov.tw/jdg/api/JDocFile/HLDM/110%2c%e7%8e%89%e5%8e%9f%e7%b0%a1%2c10%2c20211110%2c1/pdf"},"JID":"HLDM,110,玉原簡,10,20211110,1","JYEAR":"110","JCASE":"玉原簡","JNO":"10","JDATE":"20211110","JTITLE":"竊盜"}